                    <span>After reading the GOF patterns book I felt I was ready to tackle on more patterns and bought this book. This book made me feel dumb for a while for after repeated readings I still couldn't understand what the author is talking about. Finally decided to research on what other people thought about this book. Glad to find mostly negative comments in this review section for it proves i'm not dumb.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Trash</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
